author: Yelena Dzhanova
title: Rhode Island is the latest state to postpone its 2020 primary as coronavirus outbreak spreads
description: Rhode Island will move its 2020 primary to June 2 from the originally planned April 28 in response to the deadly coronavirus outbreak, Gov. Gina Raimondo announced on Monday.
content:
